1. e4 { You know how to play the opening now! } 1... e5 2. Nf3 { Develop initiation! } 2... Nf6 3. Nxe5 { NOW! } 3... Nc6?! 4. Nxc6 dxc6 5. d3 { Develop the bishop in the f file. } 5... Bc5 { This move is CRUICAL! } 6. Bg5?? { Ignore the relative pin on the knight! } 6... Nxe4!! 7. Bxd8 $140 { They think it's free... It is! We just compensate with mating the opponent! } 7... Bxf2+ (7... Nxf2 { This one is also good but it doesn't lead to mate in two }) 8. Ke2 $7 { This is their only move! } 8... Bg4# *


